snippet.title: Apples to Apples PS3 Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a just a video showing off the new cool game Apples to Apples. This is a really fun game that lets you play with words.

Feel free to comment and leave any tips you have for Apples to Apples.

Thanks for watching!

Recorded with my new Hauppauge HD DVR :-)
